item.title: When I Attempted Infographics
item.description: Once upon a time between 2015 and 2016, I organized an informal San Diego meetup group among my immediate contacts for “young ocean conservation & science professionals” (wow what a mouthful) and I made these wonderful AMATEUR infographics. Really I just wanted to drink beer and talk about the ocean.
